data.description: This lovely 1,833 sqft home with 3 beds and 2 baths rests down a quiet road on a 3.1 acre lot. Lots of nature and peace and quiet around this home. Yet it is a quick drive from Crowley and I-10. The home has a large storage building/workshop that could be used in a variety of ways and it has electricity running to it. Additionally, the home has two fenced in areas. One directly behind the home and a second at the back of the property and this one is electrified. Great if you have farm animals that you want to keep safe. This home comes with the refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, stove, washer and dryer, deep freezer, two hutches and security system as well. The home has new floors in one guest bedroom and in the primary bathroom. Home being sold as is.
